  entries:
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 2962d3bb5774ee54dbb2dafb1061cc4c, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 10709f25d15216f4f98d30122c07885e, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 795521f822b7f5f44a05e943484eb0f9, type: 3}
    description: Cunning scavengers clad in ragged bone armor. They strike from the brush,
      vanish into the trees, and return in hungry packs whenever gold or easy prey is near.
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fd185a011d84a7842acc9baa4703ff70, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3c0e880bf4c60cc48bae36f9e273bdf0, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a704fa612dd835041a682d7153ee2c2f, type: 3}
    description: Ancient bones that refuse the grave. Bound by lingering hate, these
      silent warriors rise again with rusted blades until their cursed remains are finally
      shattered.
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c9f6b4d3a51e6872f4a3b2c0d5e7f1a0, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a1bd940a63fe7a34093318310d9c3ecb, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f5be83e45fa503747a4dad467928e3f6, type: 3}
    description: A mischievous little demon that thrives on chaos and fear. Quick and
      slippery, it burns and teases travelers, then slips into shadow before heavier foes
      arrive.
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fe68915e9adde944997b2a3d790af38c, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4ba16ad3bb75bbd43a62af81d5adc1e4, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a842cf257ff62d34592611ad95594700, type: 3}
    description: A fierce beast of the deep forest. Thick fur and crushing paws make
      it deadly on the trail; once provoked, it charges without mercy until the threat
      is gone.
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b2c3d4e5f6789012345678cafe002003, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9b063c9bed9540b478f1674b6f204fd7, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 161d1196880d3a24d81481414469cc65, type: 3}
    description: A lesser stone construct with glowing veins of restless magic. Smaller
      than its kin, yet stubborn in battle, it guards ruins and broken shrines with relentless
      force.
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4c9638b359b7dd34e8adc91ba1a07a8b, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3ff32c28e3f2819448eb14d543dba18d, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6a709a27c0a341e41a2bafbf0afdd89b, type: 3}
    description: A brutal warlord of the orc tribes. Clad for war and hungry for conquest,
      it leads crushing raids across the land and drives weaker creatures from its path.
  - stats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9012345678abcd, type: 2}
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e6bfd5e4bb6175e42a738e08f629f40a, type: 3}
    listIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: de000b81cfd4c184b87aa6c8eea6fb6b, type: 3}
    description: An ancient guardian of living stone. Forged to watch forgotten places,
      its glowing eyes never sleep, and every heavy step shakes the ground until intruders
      fall or flee.
